  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vladimere's Lhore is a collection of games including 14 games from said developer, spanning a wide variety of genres. Including; Stalker Horror, 3D Platformer, Combat Flight Sim, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is also a museum full of facts about each game and developers commentary hiding within them where Vladimere Lhore talks about their thought process : </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>KILLDEATH</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"When a mortal coil begins to fail, the only recourse is to KILLDEATH itself and gain immortality.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980710/extras/KILLDEATH.PNG?t=1770133841\" /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An Atari 2600 style Action game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expected Play Time : 10-15 minutes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill Death before the clock runs out. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill Demons for a precious few extra seconds. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>No Strings Attached</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"A night of noodles and canoodles is cut short by a demon from the past.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980710/extras/No_Strings_Attached.PNG?t=1770133841\" /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An 8-bit Stalker Horror.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expected Play Time : 45-90 minutes  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock the secrets of the estate. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try not to get caught. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Hellenore</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Hellenore is looking to get out of the house when her friend Haru asks for help.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980710/extras/Hellenore.PNG?t=1770133841\" /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute 3D Platformer.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expected Play Time : 30-60 minutes  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 Levels to explore. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Nightmare Killer</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"A dream that feels a little too real.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980710/extras/15b118953f58cf9d908a265c74a94b62.avif?t=1770133841\" width=500 height=250 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A PS1 style Comedy Horror.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expected Play Time : 5-10 minutes  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore Hallways. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Read Notes. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Out run the Killer. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape the Nightmare. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>KILLDEATH Again</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"When a mortal coil begins to fail, the only recourse is to kill Death itself and gain immortality.... again\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980710/extras/500b956908a2b58a0fc1186880f5328d.avif?t=1770133841\" width=500 height=250 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A PS1 style ARPG.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expected Play Time : 15-30 minutes  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill Death before the clock runs out.... Again </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect Upgrades. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slay swarms of Husks with the Harvester Flame. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Become Prey</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Barbara Jones recalls the reasons why she doesn't camp alone anymore.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980710/extras/8dbb629b9b792f38d7d9cc2dc620324c.avif?t=1770133841\" width=500 height=250 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A PS1 style Natural Horror game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expected Play Time : 10-20 minutes  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the woods. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid becoming prey. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Become Prey 2</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Barbara Jones fights for her life as old trauma rears its ugly head.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980710/extras/0b0684c29e66d6f8664ac4b0203b4897.avif?t=1770133841\" width=500 height=250 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A PS1 style Action Horror.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expected Play Time : 60-90 minutes  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight coyotes. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect gems. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade rifle. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 Levels. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>What A Wonderful Life</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Remember the past in a sea of memories.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980710/extras/4af90b2aa87792c8d171eee0686644dd.avif?t=1770133841\" width=500 height=250 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A PS1 style Psychological Horror</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expected Play Time : 10-20 minutes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drive a boat. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remember what was. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the atmosphere.  </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>The Arrogance Of Man</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"A machine freezes over, the flesh follows.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980710/extras/cd19d49c8dc13acfcdd6a77182af0e9f.avif?t=1770133841\" width=500 height=250 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A PS2 style eco-Horror.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expected Play Time : 10-15 minutes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stave off the cold with flares. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put off the inevitable.  </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Arcade Woah!!!</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Free play is forever, it only costs your soul.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980710/extras/f2d9c1a266d4f82f22f4cdb0723e12a6.avif?t=1770133841\" width=500 height=250 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hang out at the hottest arcade in Hell.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expected Play Time : 30-60 minutes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play some Asteroids. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your reflexes on Typhoon. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Toadle cross the road. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect tickets. Buy prizes. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Madvent 2&3</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Catch up on Madvent lore and stop Necrosis before it's too late.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980710/extras/Madvent_2_3.PNG?t=1770133841\" /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fly through New Spook City in the Flight Combat Sim we have at home.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expected Play Time : 10-20 minutes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take out the towers before time runs out. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>C.H.A.I.N.G.E.D. : Unbound</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Explore a lost branch from the critically acclaimed C.H.A.I.N.G.E.D..\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980710/extras/499133a459c78026da7039a4918288b7.avif?t=1770133841\" width=500 height=250 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PS1 Horror Adventure</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expected Play Time : 30-45 minutes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Protect your daughter at all costs. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Live up to your name sake, God Killer. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Madvent 4 : End Of The Line</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Take a trip with friends to the North Pole to fix what's broken..\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980710/extras/90f9f4c0eb76b4e44a5328b70b80afe8.avif?t=1770133841\" width=500 height=250 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Walking Sim</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expected Play Time : 30-45 minutes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore up to 8 locations! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Catch up with your monstrous pals! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy it while it lasts! </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Make Beautiful</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"The flesh you were born with doesn't have to be the flesh you die in.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980710/extras/3602727997420a5b6f682c8495d34daf.avif?t=1770133841\" width=500 height=250 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Horror Visual Novel.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expected Play Time : 15-30 minutes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your ideal self.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore an eerie facility.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So many ways to die!</p></li></ul>",
