e and stop Necrosis before it's too late.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980710/extras/Madvent_2_3.PNG?t=1770133841\" /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fly through New Spook City in the Flight Combat Sim we have at home.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expected Play Time : 10-20 minutes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take out the towers before time runs out. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>C.H.A.I.N.G.E.D. : Unbound</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Explore a lost branch from the critically acclaimed C.H.A.I.N.G.E.D..\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980710/extras/499133a459c78026da7039a4918288b7.avif?t=1770133841\" width=500 height=250 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PS1 Horror Adventure</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expected Play Time : 30-45 minutes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Protect your daughter at all costs. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Live up to your name sake, God Killer. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Madvent 4 : End Of The Line</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Take a trip with friends to the North Pole to fix what's broken..\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980710/extras/90f9f4c0eb76b4e44a5328b70b80afe8.avif?t=1770133841\" width=500 height=250 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Walking Sim</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expected Play Time : 30-45 minutes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore up to 8 locations! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Catch up with your monstrous pals! 